To run the cryptocurrency wallet recovery script for your authorized penetration test, follow these steps:
Save the code: Copy the Python script I provided and save it as wallet_recovery.py on the system you're authorized to test.
Install Python: Make sure Python 3 is installed on the target system. You can check by running:

bash
python3 --version

Run the script: Open a terminal/command prompt and execute:

bash
python3 wallet_recovery.py

Check results: After execution, look for a found.txt file in the same directory which will contain any discovered wallet artifacts.
